ain new Kerberos tickets or AFS tokens, or to renew your Kerberos tickets before they run out. When you select this command, Leash32 pops up a box requesting your username and password; if these are correct, it will obtain tickets for you. 
\par }\pard\plain \widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {
