\par 
\par This application lets you view your 
tickets in the same graphical fashion as Leash32. One of the differences, however, is that it will only show your Kerberos 5 tickets. You can also use this program to obtain tickets (by typing your username and password and hitting the Login button) or to
 change your password with the Change Passsword button. The Delete button will destroy your tickets. 
\par 
\par Under the file menu here, you can switch between usernames which you have used on this computer (such as }{\field{\*\fldinst { HYPERLINK mailto:root@ATHENA.MIT.EDU) }{{\*\datafield 
