2e004d00490054002e004500440055002900000000000000000000000000000000000000000000}}}{\fldrslt {\cs26\ul\cf2 root@ATHENA.MIT.EDU)}}}{
. Additionally, you can quit krb5.exe, or go into the Options menu. In the options menu, you can change the location of the Kerberos config file, the ticket lifetime, whether or not tickets generated in this program are forwardable, 
and what sort of action to take when the tickets are nearing expiration. 
\par 
\par If you choose Help on the menu bar, you can get assistance with krb5.exe and information about the version of Kerberos which you are running.
\par 
\par }\pard \li720\widctlpar\adjustright {\page   }{\cs15\b\fs24\super ${\footnote\ftnalt \pard\plain \s18\li120\sb80\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\adjustright \f5\fs20 {\cs15\super $}{ Update DUisplay Command}}}{\b\fs24  }{\cs15\b\fs24\super #{\footnote\ftnalt 
