\par 
\par }\pard \widctlpar\outlinelevel0\adjustright {\b How It Works...}{
\par }\pard \widctlpar\adjustright {While Leash32 automatically checks the status of your Kerberos tickets every 30 seconds, the Update Display command forces an immediate status check.
